Put the controller on the sidetable.

Take the controller from the couch.

high_descs: Turn around then right to walk out the doorway. Walk up to the gray couch against the back wall.
Pick up the black controller on the couch cushion.
Turn left then right to center yourself in front of the side table next to the couch.
Place the black controller to the left of the coffee mug on the side table.
Turn around and walk right out of the doorway. Once through, turn right to face the brown desk against the wall.
Pick up the black controller on the desk.
Hold the controller from the side table, turn right, walk out the doorway, then left and face the side table.
Place the black controller on top of the other black controller on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put the two controller on the side table.
